snippet: Milos Raonic won the Brisbane International in Australia, defeating top-seeded Roger Federer, 6-4, 6-4, and reversing the outcome of their meeting in last year’s final....
lead_paragraph: Milos Raonic won the Brisbane International in Australia, defeating top-seeded Roger Federer, 6-4, 6-4, and reversing the outcome of their meeting in last year’s final.
abstract: Milos Raonic defeats Roger Federer to win Brisbane International tennis tournament; other tennis matches noted.
